sources.title: A Doggone Christmas | Full Christmas Movie | Hallmark
sources.description:
A Doggone Christmas - When the CIA discovers a cute orphan puppy with amazing telepathic abilities, the powers-that-be in Washington immediately lock him down and plan on forcing the poor dog to become a covert secret weapon. But fate steps in and frees the pint-sized Jack Russel Terrier from government clutches - delivering the cute little fellow into the loving arms of two brothers just a week before Christmas.
2016. Stars: Jaret Sacrey, Zachary Cirino, Dominique Swain
